      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        The CSV files you upload need to follow a certain format. If you need the templates, download them here:<br>
        <%= link_to "Indicators Template", template_downloader_path(filename: 'Indicators_Template'), :method => :get, :class => "btn" %><br>
        <%= link_to "Resources Template", template_downloader_path(filename: 'Resource_Template'), :method => :get, :class => "btn" %><br>
        <%= link_to "Relationships Template", template_downloader_path(filename: 'Relationships_Template'), :method => :get, :class => "btn" %><br>
